  "title": "fix(refinementList): hide facets based on `renderingContent` when searched",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\n[CR-8645]\r\n\r\nThis PR enables facets to still be hidden when they are searched from the refinementList search box. With the isolated index change, the helper should have the `searchForFacetValues` fn defined. This prevents the `lastResults` from being null like it was the case for the `mainHelper`.\r\n\r\nAlso fixed helper tests which wrongly passed due to array splicing logic that was used before.\r\n\r\n\r\n[CR-8645]: https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/CR-8645?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNWRkNTljNzYxNjVmNDY3MDlhMDU5Y2ZhYzA5YTRkZjUiLCJwIjoiZ2l0aHViLWNvbS1KU1cifQ",
